    public abstract class TransactionBuilder<B extends TransactionBuilder<B,​T>,​T extends Transaction>
extends java.lang.Object
    Transaction builder is base class implementing builder pattern to construct instance of transaction. It is bases of specialized transaction builders for all types of transactions
